Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat {\i1}this{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Mega Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As great as I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to that {\i1}kid{\i0}...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the winner is... Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I DID IT~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, excusing the interruption that just occurred,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we shall now begin the final round of the tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...featuring Yugi Mutou versus Katsuya Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the time has finally come...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Final Game of Friendship!\N Yugi VS Jounouchi (Part 1)"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall now commence with the final round of the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:02:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final round will feature Yugi Mutou versus Katsuya Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you'll surely save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well then, bye bye, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just clean it up. It's disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the Duelist Kingdom finals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would come down to Yugi-kun and Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True... but a match is a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got to fight each other seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi would give the prize money to Jounouchi after he wins...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do they still have to fight each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't have a match, they can't get the prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true and all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are best friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For those two to seriously fight each other...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's {\i1}why{\i0} they're going to fight each other seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what best friends do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, don't even tell me you can't Duel against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've fought a lot of difficult battles to make it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who the opponent is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we made it this far because we fought on to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-kun's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've got to fight until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the sake of everything we've fought for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now accept this match with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you have both done Well winning and making it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a battle to determine who earns the privilege of challenging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So go forth and fight on with everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna say something before we start the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe this or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually made it all the way to the final round, against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it this far thanks to you and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm feeling something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I really wanna fight you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you have incredible strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to fight head on against this strength, against this {\i1}power{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Duelist's flame is starting to ignite within Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:05:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flame that aches to fight against a strong opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is truly remarkable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despite the two having such a strong friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they are able to cast away their feelings as a friend and can charge in head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is truly the most fitting match for the final round of the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-kun, I'm not holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm giving it my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, I'll beat you and that incredible power of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'll do it in the name of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start things off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Swordsman in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and Jounouchi both have the same goal... to save someone precious to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something completely different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, those two are fighting their strongest as Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're putting all that to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what makes them men!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if Jounouchi-kun's usual head-on attack pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be enough to take down Yugi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a truly beautiful sight this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, the Duel Ring is like a pen holding two wild beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's your turn, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Mage Knight Giltia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magical Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Swordsman just got a beatin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out something more powerful than {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's really gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Duel's just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to focus, Yugi-kun's got the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Yugi-kun's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's hiding his fighting spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while observing Jounouchi-kun at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The old Jounouchi-kun would charge in with raw power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the Jounouchi-kun in front of me is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's fought many battles, and he's learned the importance of strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He almost seems like another person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this game, each battle between Monsters is a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I play a Monster with higher Attack than yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may only win one battle, and the lead can change at any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned quite a bit since I came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fully aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to Duel Monsters is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a balance between Magic Cards and Monster Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One who is unaware of this has no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've learned a lot from watching your matches, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should know not to use up all your good Monster Cards right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Thanks for that little piece of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Knight Gaia in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mage Knight Giltia has been beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, now that's what I'm talkin' about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm different than I used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armored Lizard, in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it's a plan to lure me into attacking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's that Jounouchi up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Jounouchi-kun seems to be planning something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon's Summon, in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Lightning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I beat Armored Lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all a part of Jounouchi-kun's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just being beaten left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun was trying to lure Yugi-kun out and make him lose focus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by playing a mediocre card from his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew his opponent wasn't going to play a strong Monster from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he played Armored Lizard in order to force him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you would wait for me to play something stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the moment you brought out the Demon's Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A balance between Magic Cards and Monster Cards is the most important thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna return that advice to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play the Flame Swordsman in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Jounouchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can win with Attack Points like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Card Shield in the Right Hand, Sword in the Left Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he played that card, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card switched the Attack and Defense Power of every Monster on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your Attack Power now becomes 1200.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my Attack Power is now 1600!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Spirit Flame Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just beat the Demon's Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Armored Lizard really was bait to lure my Demon Skull out...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, the only way to beat {\i1}you{\i0} is to take one Monster on at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really have grown, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a splendid combination of Monster Cards and Magic Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear you praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi really {\i1}has{\i0} gotten so much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm-hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's grown {\i1}this{\i0} much,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he may actually have a chance against Yugi-kun after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They both know what the other is thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and they know each other's strategies to a Tee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is truly worthy of praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get serious, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come at me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse of Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the Fusion card,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I polymerize Curse of Dragon with Dark Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Gaia, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Swordsman is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fierce attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun has been observing how Jounouchi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,plays up until now - his playing pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like he's finally gotten serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Jounouchi wouldn't want it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is almost like two wild animals fighting instinct against instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, there wouldn't be a need for such big attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They both just want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yugi and Jounouchi fighting down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do those two have to fight each other in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just {\i1}because{\i0} they're Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regardless of who your opponent is, once you enter the ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you must fight until the opponent falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is what defines the world of Duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel is only going to get more intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no one can stop those two now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what're you going to do, Jounouchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and beat my Dragon Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get a hold of yourself, Katsuya Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to focus on destroying Dragon Knight Gaia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What happens after that doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dragon Knight Gaia has 2600 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my strongest Monster, the Red-Eyes Black Dragon, only has 2400 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I play it, my chances of winning will only decrease...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's these moments that makes Dueling so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi boy is rustling up all of his offensive power,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}trying to think of a plan to destroy Yugi boy's Dragon Knight Gaia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even with all his might, such a task is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What tricks will you use to get out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A head-on attack will only get him killed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to use a Magic Card combo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to make my Red-Eyes more powerful than the Dragon Knight Gaia Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But is there even a way to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, but once I enter the ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not lose, by any means necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll use any methods necessary to block any attempt you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now... What will you try next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I {\b0}do{\b1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Mimic Illusionist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Imitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Graverobber!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I use the both of these,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can beat the Dragon Knight Gaia's 2600 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did he think up a strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might be a {\i1}genius{\i0} here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...came up with a way to destroy your Dragon Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun came up with a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\s1}Trap{\s0} Magic Card, Graverobber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lets me steal a card from your Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be takin' the Demon's Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'm gonna use the same strategy you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the Mimic Illusionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lets me copy one of the opponent's cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I'm gonna copy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fusion card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've ever used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's effect is really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fuse the Demon's Summon with the Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Skull Dragon - Black Demon's Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Demon's Dragon, rip Dark Knight Gaia apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beat Dark Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I said this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I was gonna beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi. I finally understand the true fun in Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is a true Duel, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen in this Duel...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who know that are those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling we'll find out soon enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one thing's for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two will keep fighting until one of them falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a site truly worthy of my eyes to behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(139,143)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do those two have to fight such an heated Duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While viewing Yugi and Jounouchi pushing themselves to the limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've slowly begun to understand how the two feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which of you win, your Life hasn't truly fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Final Game of Friendship! Yugi VS Jounouchi (Part 2)"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:21:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:22:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
